                        <a href="https://www.sharevault.com/resources/glossary" class="text-muted" target="_blank">Glossary</a>&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;|&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;
